About Pratiksha CHS
Pratiksha CHS StatusUnder Construction
Pratiksha CHS is a well-planned project that is ideally positioned in Bhandup East, Mumbai. The address of this smartly planned project is Nahur East, Bhandup East, Mumbai, Maharashtra, India. . The pin code of this masterpiece project is 400078.
